The Plan, previously known as Plan B, is a Saudi burger outlet located in Jeddah and inspired by the Tex-Mex fusion.
	Its menu consists of various options for appetizers ranging from tacos to saucy bites, and even a salad option.
	The eatery aims to offer a range of beef and chicken burgers with balanced taste and texture on soft, crunchy buns.
	Desserts include a creamy ice cream topped with a sprinkle of Cerelac.
